  <brief_title>HPA Axis Study in Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Open Label Study to Evaluate the Adrenal Suppression Potential of Mapracorat 0.1% Ointment in Adults With Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
