  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter, open-label study to evaluate the adrenal suppression potential of Mapracorat
      0.1% ointment in adults with atopic dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of safety, efficacy, pharmacokinetics and adrenal suppression potential of
      Mapracorat 0.1% ointment in adults with atopic dermatitis.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
