  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Signed written informed consent

          -  Male or female subject aged &gt;= 18 years

          -  Diagnosis of atopic dermatitis according to Hanifin and Rajka Criteria

          -  Investigator's Global Assessment (IGA) score of 3 (moderate) to 4 (severe) at baseline

          -  Normal ACTH response before start of treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy or lactation

          -  Clinically relevant disease, which could interfere with the study conduct or the
             evaluation and interpretation of the study results

          -  Concomitant medical or dermatological disorder(s), which could interfere with the
             study conduct or the evaluation and interpretation of the study results

          -  Clinically manifest immunosuppressive disorder or known history of malignant disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
